collections.name: Ape in 2025
collections.description: "A detailed black-and-white illustration of a fierce-looking anthropomorphic monkey wearing a backward baseball cap, large hoop earrings, and a thick chain necklace. The monkey has deep, expressive wrinkles on its face, a serious and intense gaze, and a rough, textured fur pattern. It is dressed in a quilted leather jacket with visible stitching and metallic buttons. The overall style is a blend of hand-drawn etching and street art, with high contrast shading and fine linework."

collections.name: Beyond the Facade
collections.description: Beyond the Facade is a visual exploration of the inner conflicts and hidden identities that lie beneath the surface. At its core, a mask represents the facade we present to the world, while the surrounding elements reveal the complexities of our true selves. The piece delves into the tension between outward appearances and the deeper truths that are often concealed. Through symbolic elements and cosmic patterns, the artwork invites viewers to reflect on their own masks and the unseen battles within. It is a journey into the soul, challenging the viewer to look beyond the surface and confront the hidden realities of human existence.

collections.name: NEW
collections.description: The “NEW” collection features 10,000 AI-generated abstract artworks, and each NFT grants a unique opportunity: access to a mysterious future collection by the same creator. However, this journey into the unknown requires a definitive choice. When you choose to receive a work from the new collection, the original “NEW” NFT is permanently deleted and you lose access to the previous piece forever. The decision between retaining ownership of the “NEW” abstract artwork or sacrificing that ownership to explore and acquire the new collection is irrevocable. Once you make your decision, the portal to “NEW” mercilessly closes. The question looms in the air: the comfort of the known or the irresistible lure of the unknown, even if the price is eternal loss? The choice between the secure possession of NEW and the leap of faith into the next collection is an irrevocable pact with the future. What are you willing to lose to unlock the secrets that have yet to be written?

collections.name: Crazy Knight Curve
collections.description:
In the grand chessboard of randomness, a lone knight embarks on a chaotic journey—
Leaping through an unseen labyrinth, tracing a spectral dance upon the digital canvas.
Each step, dictated by fate, bends the arc of motion into a tangled elegance.
A curve emerges—not drawn, but discovered—woven from the whispers of unpredictability.

"Crazy Knight Curve" is a generative artwork created using p5.js, inspired by the erratic yet structured movement of a chess knight. The piece evolves from a series of constrained random choices, forming an intricate, curvilinear path across a dynamically sized grid.

The process begins with:

A randomly determined grid (5 to 300 columns and rows).

A knight that moves in an unconventional step size, dictated by two randomly selected offsets (s1, s2).

A defined number of steps, which are executed as long as valid moves exist.

The knight's movement follows a modified L-shaped pattern, with possible steps dynamically filtered to remain within the grid's boundaries. Each successive point in the journey is connected through a smooth Bézier-style interpolation (curveVertex), softening the rigid chess-like motion into a fluid, organic form.

Visually, the artwork balances geometric precision with chaotic spontaneity, creating a path that is at once structured and free-flowing—a perfect paradox of order and disorder.

These characters are brought to life through a curated collection of NFTs, featuring artworks inspired by the timeless aesthetics of Studio Ghibli. Each piece invites collectors to delve into the rich narratives and artistic beauty of the Peenarverse.
